  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Update SOP Makeree</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="SV">Uppdatering SOP Makerere - direktupphandling</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="SV">PLEASE REVIEW YOUR ANSWER AS THE QUESTION HAS BEEN CHANGED

Makereres Standard Operating Procedure beh&#xF6;ver uppdateras inf&#xF6;r nytt avtal 2015-2020 - en direktupphandling har genomf&#xF6;rts f&#xF6;r att utf&#xF6;ra detta uppdrag d&#xE4;r 3 firmor tillfr&#xE5;gats, PwC; Deloitte och RSM och d&#xE4;r PwC l&#xE4;mnat det mest f&#xF6;rdelaktiga beslutet</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The consultant shall produce one single, stand alone, steering document for the prospective Uganda-Sweden research training partnership program 2015-2020. The consultant shall produce the document through updating and harmonizing relevant manuals and guidelines, updating obsolete data in the manuals and guidelines at hand, and adding currently missing information.

The assignment is a direct procurement since there is no framework agreement that covers these services is in place. The same firms as we have framework agreement with for audit services have been asked, i.e. PwC, Deloitte and RSM - see contr number 51180080. The assignment is estimated to take approximately 150 hours and shall be conducted during the months of June to August 2015.</narrative>
  </description>
